  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Fatherhood",
  "purpose": "The APPG for Fatherhood will seek opportunities for policy and legislative review to identify and improve the statutory and social frameworks affecting families. This will be in order to help reduce the barriers fathers face to playing a full and positive role in their children’s lives.",
